{"id":"lyr_5rOz5YS__MTc0MA_0021","text":"如爲你哭泣不緊要","structure":{"line_index":21,"char_count":8},"semantics":{"themes":["付出","愛情","不在乎"],"sentiment":"NEUTRAL","keywords":["哭泣","緊要"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[0,5,3,3,3,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["jyu4","nei5","huk1","jap1","bat1","gan2","jiu3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"如爲","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"你","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"哭泣","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"緊要","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"簡短的句子，再次強調為對方付出（哭泣）並不在乎是否重要。"},"source":{"title":"一時倦了","artists":["泳兒"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1740","prev_line_id":"lyr_5rOz5YS__MTc0MA_0020","next_line_id":"lyr_5rOz5YS__MTc0MA_0022","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5rOz5YS__MTc0MA_0022","text":"但我面對心裏面全部需要 還是需要","structure":{"line_index":22,"char_count":15},"semantics":{"themes":["面對","需求","掙扎"],"sentiment":"NEGATIVE","keywords":["面對","心裏","需要","還是"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,5,2,4,3,5,2,0,2,3,4,0,2,3,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["daan6","ngo5","min6","deoi3","sam1","leoi5","min6","cyun4","bou6","seoi1","jiu3","waan4","si6","seoi1","jiu3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"但","pos":"CONJ"},{"text":"我","pos":"PRON"},{"text":"面對","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"心裏","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"面","pos":"PART"},{"text":"全部","pos":"DET"},{"text":"需要","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"還是","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"需要","pos":"VERB"}],"syntax_notes":"「但」字轉折，表達了即使嘴上說不在乎，內心深處卻仍然有需求，顯示內心的掙扎。"},"source":{"title":"一時倦了","artists":["泳兒"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1740","prev_line_id":"lyr_5rOz5YS__MTc0MA_0021","next_line_id":"lyr_5rOz5YS__MTc0MA_0023","paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
{"id":"lyr_5rOz5YS__MTc0MA_0023","text":"若愛依然重要 就算失戀不緊要","structure":{"line_index":23,"char_count":13},"semantics":{"themes":["愛情","重要性","接受"],"sentiment":"POSITIVE","keywords":["若愛","重要","失戀","緊要"]},"prosody":{"tone_pattern":[2,4,3,0,4,2,4,3,9,3,9,4],"tone_pattern_cantonese_jyutping":["joek6","oi3","ji1","jin4","jiu3","zau6","syun3","sat1","lyun2","bat1","gan2","jiu3"]},"nlp":{"tokens":[{"text":"若愛","pos":"VERB"},{"text":"依然","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"重要","pos":"ADJ"},{"text":"就算","pos":"ADP"},{"text":"失戀","pos":"NOUN"},{"text":"不","pos":"ADV"},{"text":"緊要","pos":"ADJ"}],"syntax_notes":"「若愛依然重要」是關鍵的轉變，即使經歷失戀，只要愛本身仍然重要，那麼失戀的痛苦也就不再重要，語氣趨於釋然。"},"source":{"title":"一時倦了","artists":["泳兒"],"lyricists":["周耀輝"],"year":0,"genre":["Cantopop","Ballad"]},"context_links":{"doc_id":"feitsui_1740","prev_line_id":"lyr_5rOz5YS__MTc0MA_0022","next_line_id":null,"paragraph_id":"para_06"}}
